replies.body:
I'm glad you were able to finally get logged in!
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 

For future reference, getting stuck on the authentication step is a pretty good sign that your network is having a hard time communicating with our login servers. Be sure to check the steps [**here**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) for some quick fixes if that happens again!
